															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610249682" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;" >A Random Day</a></span> <span class="odate time_1584224184 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">14 Mar 2020 22:16</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4547793">
									

<p>A milestone and a half. In the four and a half years since I wrote this piece, Santosh has gone on to become a full-blown character in his own right — partly through my own <a href="/moonlighting">Moonlighting</a> but mostly through <span class="printuser"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirpudding" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(348648); return false;">sirpudding</a></span>’s excellent work on <a href="/scp-2111">Ara Orun</a>. Arvind, meanwhile, has fallen into obscurity — and perhaps that’s what he deserves and wants, to be eclipsed by his own son.</p>

							</div>

								
