			<div class="content" id="post-content-2413559">
									

<p>Thanks Gaffney. I've spent a lot of time wondering how to introduce Arvind Ramkumar Desai as a character into the Foundation, and your praise really means a lot.</p>
<p>I struggled with that last letter; wondering if it spelled out the issue too much or not.<br />
I'm not proud of this, but those letters are patterned after my own relationship with my father, questions about a girl friend, brusque replies, and all. I don't really know what else to say&#8230;</p>
<p>Thanks Gaffney. Means a lot.</p>

