														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2416680">
									

<p>There are two key arcs which are connected.</p>
<p>The first arc involves Arvind trying and failing to reconnect with his estranged son Santosh. This arc is composed of the letters between Santosh and Arvind, which are interspersed between the email exchanges in the second arc to maintain the reader's emotional investment.</p>
<p>The second arc is Arvind deciding to become a mole for the GOC in order to stop Alpha-9, recalling how Santosh's death was caused in part by the existence of Omega-7 and fueled by the desire to prevent more deaths from occurring at the hands of Alpha-9.</p>

							</div>

								
					
